(20, 23, 'How to find a target audience', 'video', '5621728901928.mp4', NULL, NULL, '8:57', '12370211', '2024-10-14 02:16:54', '2024-10-14 17:32:08', NULL),
(21, 24, 'Tools for social media management', 'text', NULL, NULL, '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019466876983641;margin-left: 72.2750015258789pt;margin-right: 1.9232177734375pt;text-indent: 0.43999481201171875pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Social media management plays a crucial role in effectively managing and growing a brand\'s presence on various social media platforms and it can sometimes be overwhelming. To achieve this, social media managers rely on a variety of tools that help streamline their workflow, enhance content creation and scheduling, analyze performance, engage with the community, and more.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019479751586914;margin-left: 72.22000122070312pt;margin-right: 4.2681884765625pt;text-indent: 0.4069976806640625pt;margin-top:18.7354736328125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">These tools are like helpful assistants that make it easier to organize, schedule, and analyze your social media activities. In this lesson, we will explore different tools that can simplify your social media management tasks.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 91.26499938964844pt;margin-top:36.36383056640625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">1. Content Creation Tools:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019452571868895;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 2.67852783203125pt;margin-top:4.791534423828125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Canva: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.canva.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> This tool allows you to create eye-catching graphics and designs for your social media posts, even if you have no design experience. </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Adobe Spark: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.adobe.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Similar to Canva, Adobe Spark offers easy-to-use design features to create visually appealing images, videos, and web pages for social media.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 90.6709976196289pt;margin-top:36.363922119140625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">2. Scheduling and Publishing:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019466876983641;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 1.62652587890625pt;text-indent: -17.26300048828125pt;margin-top:4.791473388671875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.26300048828125pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Hootsuite: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.hootsuite.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Hootsuite enables you to schedule and publish your social media posts in advance, saving you time and effort. It supports multiple social media platforms, allowing you to manage all your accounts from one place.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019479751586914;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 3.2901611328125pt;text-indent: -17.31800079345703pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:1.10693359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.31800079345703pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Buffer: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.buffer.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Buffer is another popular scheduling tool that allows you to plan and schedule posts across different social media platforms. It also provides analytics to track your post performance.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019462585449218;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 4.27288818359375pt;text-indent: -17.680999755859375pt;margin-top:1.106964111328125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.680999755859375pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Later: (</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.later.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The \"Later\" app is a popular scheduling tool that helps you plan and schedule your social media posts in advance. It is designed to simplify the process of managing and organizing your content across various social media platforms, including Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, and Pinterest.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 90.5719985961914pt;margin-top:36.36387634277344pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">3. Social Media Analytics Tools:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019506931304932;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 7.591064453125pt;text-indent: -17.593002319335938pt;margin-top:4.791473388671875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.593002319335938pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Facebook Insights: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">If you\'re using Facebook, Facebook Insights provides valuable data about your audience, post reach, engagement, and more. It helps you understand what content resonates with your audience.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019479751586914;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 2.26959228515625pt;text-indent: -17.031997680664062pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.031997680664062pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Instagram Insights: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">For Instagram, Instagram Insights offers similar information, such as post reach, impressions, profile visits, and audience demographics. It helps you measure your Instagram success.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019442558288575;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 7.0205078125pt;text-indent: -17.26300048828125pt;margin-top:1.10693359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.26300048828125pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Google Analytics: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Google Analytics is a powerful tool that provides in-depth insights into your website\'s traffic and social media referral data. It helps you understand how your social media efforts contribute to website visits and conversions.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019462585449218;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 9.0460205078125pt;text-indent: -17.31800079345703pt;margin-top:1.1070556640625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.31800079345703pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Sprout Social: (</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.sproutsocial.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Sprout Social offers comprehensive analytics across multiple social media platforms. It provides detailed reports on engagement, audience demographics, and post performance, helping you track your overall social media success.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 90.04399871826172pt;margin-top:36.3638916015625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">4. Social Listening and Engagement Tools:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019423961639403;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 16.51519775390625pt;text-indent: -17.26300048828125pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:4.791534423828125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.26300048828125pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Mention: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.mention.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Mention allows you to monitor social media mentions and conversations about your brand, industry, or relevant keywords. It helps you stay informed about what people are saying and engage in conversations.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.601946973800659;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 3.63848876953125pt;text-indent: -17.394996643066406pt;margin-top:1.107025146484375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.394996643066406pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Sprout Social: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.sproutsocial.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Besides analytics, Sprout Social also offers tools for managing your social media community. It allows you to schedule and publish posts, monitor messages and comments, and engage with your audience all in one place.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019466876983641;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 34.19500732421875pt;text-indent: -17.449996948242188pt;margin-top:1.106903076171875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.449996948242188pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Hootsuite: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.hootsuite.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> In addition to scheduling, Hootsuite provides features for social media monitoring, allowing you to listen to conversations, respond to comments, and engage with your audience effectively.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 90.68199920654297pt;margin-top:36.36395263671875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">5. Social Media Advertising Tools:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019498348236083;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 18.533203125pt;text-indent: -17.031997680664062pt;margin-top:4.791351318359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.031997680664062pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Facebook Ads Manager: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.facebook.com/business/tools/ads-manager</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> If you\'re running Facebook or Instagram ads, Facebook Ads Manager provides a platform to create, manage, and track your ad campaigns. It allows you to target specific audiences, set budgets, and monitor ad performance.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ccabe2d-7fff-ae76-09ea-73419303318b\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019442558288575;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;text-indent: -17.692001342773438pt;margin-top:1.10693359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.692001342773438pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Upfluence: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.upfluence.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">) Upfluence helps you discover and connect with relevant social media influencers for potential collaborations and influencer marketing campaigns. It provides influencer data, performance metrics, and contact information.</span></p>', '', '', '2024-10-14 02:18:03', '2024-10-14 02:18:03', NULL),
